headlines.description: — Cam Johnson scored 34 points, Dennis Schroder had 14 points and 12 assists and the Brooklyn Nets beat the Charlotte Hornets 116-115 Tuesday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Cam Johnson and Dennis Schroder carry the Nets to a 116-115 win over the Hornets

headlines.description: — Jamal Murray scored 27 points, Michael Porter Jr. added 24 points and 10 rebounds as the the Denver Nuggets snapped a two-game losing streak defeating the Memphis Grizzlies 122-110 in an NBA Cup game on Tuesday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Murray, Porter lead Nuggets past Grizzlies 122-110

events.name: New Orleans Pelicans at Dallas Mavericks

headlines.description: — Luka Doncic returned to the lineup and scored a game-high 26 points, Klay Thompson added 19 and Kyrie Irving had 18 as the Dallas Mavericks beat the undermanned New Orleans Pelicans 132-91 in an NBA Cup game on Tuesday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Luka Doncic returns from injury to score 26 points as Mavericks top the Pelicans 132-91

events.name: Oklahoma City Thunder at San Antonio Spurs

headlines.description: — Keldon Johnson scored 22 points, Harrison Barnes added 20 and the San Antonio Spurs beat the Oklahoma City Thunder 110-104 Tuesday night without Victor Wembanyama for their first victory in the Emirates NBA Cup.
headlines.shortLinkText: Johnson, Barnes help Spurs fend off hard-charging Thunder for first NBA Cup victory, 110-104

events.name: Utah Jazz at Los Angeles Lakers
